00:27:36.140 --> 00:27:37.570
wondering if you can talk a little bit more
about that.

00:27:37.570 --> 00:27:41.409
Eighty percent seems like an astonishingly
high approval rating.

00:27:41.409 --> 00:27:44.259
And if true, it's remarkable and good.

00:27:44.259 --> 00:27:45.830
But I just wanted to hear your additional
thoughts on that.

00:27:45.830 --> 00:27:46.830
&gt;&gt;Ann Lee: Yes.

00:27:46.830 --> 00:27:52.669
I would be skeptical, too, if they were coming
from Chinese polling services.

00:27:52.669 --> 00:27:58.100
But this is actually coming from an American
polling service who do similar polls with

00:27:58.100 --> 00:28:05.590
Americans and find that consistently, around
