00:41:31.540 --> 00:41:33.000
things that would actually be worse.

00:41:33.000 --> 00:41:34.660
So, how do we--?

00:41:34.660 --> 00:41:39.920
&gt;&gt;Ann Lee: Well, my answer is that it always
