00:41:56.690 --> 00:42:02.070
You are the product of what is around you
and the institutions that the government have

00:42:02.070 --> 00:42:03.070
set up.

00:42:03.070 --> 00:42:04.070
All right.

00:42:04.070 --> 00:42:06.319
Well, thank you so much for your time and
